        "content": "# Chapter 1: Introduction to the Textbook\r\n\r\nThis chapter is your map for the book. It explains where the book is going, what you will build, which tools you will use, and why this material matters for business students, managers, analysts, entrepreneurs, and anyone whose work depends on data.\r\n\r\n## Chapter Files\r\n\r\n- [Main Chapter](ch01-main-2026-06-02.md)\r\n- [Let's Build](ch01-lets-build-2026-05-26.md)\r\n- [Review & Reflection](ch01-reflection-2026-05-26.md)\r\n- [Terms Treasury](ch01-terms-2026-05-30.md)\r\n- [Readiness Assessment Test](ch01-rat-2026-05-30.md)\r\n",
